Class CK_SSL3_RANDOM_DATA

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.safenetinc.jcprov.params.CK_SSL3_RANDOM_DATA

  • public class CK_SSL3_RANDOM_DATA
extends java.lang.Object
    Data used during the execution of the
    CKM.SSL3_MASTER_KEY_DERIVE
    CKM.SSL3_KEY_AND_MAC_DERIVE
    mechanisms.

    Further information is provided in the PKCS#11 standard and the Programmers Manual.
